changeset:   1684:8c8af3db6438
tag:         tip
user:        Trevor Williams <phase1geo@users.sourceforge.net>
date:        Thu Jan 07 00:50:16 2016 -0600
files:       lib/gui.tcl lib/indent.tcl lib/snippets.tcl lib/version.tcl lib/vim.tcl
description:
* Added support for tabstop and expandtab settings in Vim :set command.
* Added support for handling preference changes to Editor/SpacesPerTab to auto-update.
* Fixing snippets::handle_tab to handle the setting of expandtab properly.
* Improved :set command parser to parse multiple variables in same line.
* Fixed Vim modeline parser issue.
* Added support for 'gg' command (jumps to first character in editing buffer).
* Added support for space command (moves insertion cursor ahead by characters).
* Added support for backspace command (moves insertion cursor back by characters).


